==人造石化木==
人造石化木已在華盛頓實驗室中被製造了出來。製造過程是將小塊的松木浸入酸性液體兩天，再浸入矽溶膠中兩天，之後再於[[氬氣|氬氣]]中加熱至1400度C兩個小時。最終便可得出保留著木材原本細胞結構的[[碳化矽|碳化矽]]石化木。若是浸在[[鎢|鎢]]溶膠中，則可得出[[碳化鎢|碳化鎢]]石化木。<ref>''Petrified Wood in Days'', Physorg.com, January 25, 2005 http://www.physorg.com/news2801.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.physorg.com/news2801.html |date=20080926183249 }}</ref><ref>''Presto! Instant Petrified Wood Created in Lab'', Live Science, 27 January 2005 http://www.livescience.com/technology/050127_petrified_wood.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.livescience.com/technology/050127_petrified_wood.html |date=20080709020744 }}</ref>

